{{champion:126}} +{{champion:119}} +{{champion:122}} 

All were showing off their muscles.
Then {{champion:119}} said: Give it up. we all know who'll win.
{{champion:122}} eyetwitches as replies: Hmmh. Take away the cleavers and you're all talk.
{{champion:119}} touches his chin and smirks, then laughs: Well I'd still be able to pull something off.
As they fight with words {{champion:126}} just looks at them and drinks his coffee all calmly and snickers. He accedentally says: Well the one who would be to win would be the Protector of Piltover, ofcourse. It is in the title~
{{champion:119}} and {{champion:122}} looks to {{champion:126}} . Smirking they grap their weaponds and jumps on him.
In the blink of an eye {{champion:126}} graps his mace, switching it to crossbow, putting up his acceleration gate and runs away from them both.
{{champion:119}} throws his cleavers after {{champion:126}} , tripping him. {{champion:126}} then uses To The Skies on {{champion:119}}
{{champion:122}} right behind goes in by swinging his axe. {{champion:126}} knocks {{champion:122}} away.
Getting thrown cleavers in his face over and over he uses his electric field and goes in on {{champion:119}} 
{{champion:122}} pulls {{champion:119}} away from {{champion:126}} and goes in, fighting him head on.
{{champion:126}} knocking {{champion:122}} out of the way again. and uses Acceleration gate and shoots through it at {{champion:119}} 
{{champion:119}} Dies.
{{champion:126}} and {{champion:122}} in low health.
{{champion:126}} uses {{summoner:14}} on {{champion:122}} 
{{champion:122}} uses his ULT on {{champion:126}} 
Both dies.
